  "title": "Kitchen Helper (Cafe)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<p>· Assist the Chef in basic food/ingredient preparation including washing, peeling, cutting/slicing, chopping etc.</p>\n<p>· Wash , clean &amp; make dry the dishes, utensils, pots, pans, chopping boards, kitchen equipment etc.</p>\n<p>· Pack takeout orders for customers</p>\n<p>· Clean and sanitising the food preparation areas.</p>\n<p>· Sweeping &amp; mopping the floor and emptying rubbish bins.</p>\n<p>· Receive and store supplies &amp; food ingredients in appropriate &amp; hygienic ways.</p>\n<p>· Followed all food safety &amp; hygiene guidelines and standards.</p>\n<p>· Other duties assigned as needed</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong><br>\n • Preferably with 1 year’s relevant experience in general kitchen operations, food safety &amp; hygiene guidelines and practices, etc.</p>\n<p>• Minimum secondary school education and with a valid food safety course level 1 certificate</p>\n<p>• Willing to work on weekends and public holidays</p>\n<p>• Able to work independently and support other team members proactively</p>\n<p>in a fast-paced environment</p>",
